  <metadata>
    <name>Tour 26: Kaiserstuhl – Volcanic Hills</name>
    <desc>Ride to the Kaiserstuhl—a volcanic hill rising from the Rhine plain like a Mediterranean island, with terraced vineyards, exotic vegetation, and the warmest climate in Germany. Wine and food here are exceptional.</desc>
    <author>
      <name>Hockenheim Motorcycle Tours</name>
    </author>
  </metadata>
  <wpt lat="49.322000" lon="8.548000">
    <name>Hockenheim</name>
    <desc>Start/End</desc>
